South African Minister Seeks to Overturn Police Building Lease, Times Says

-- B y   A n t o n y   S g u a z z i n
-- 
2011-06-21T05:34:30Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-21/south-african-minister-seeks-to-overturn-police-building-lease-times-says.html
South Africa ’s Public Works Minister
Gwen Mahlangu-Nkabinde will take legal steps to have a 500
million rand police headquarters lease agreement canceled,
Johannesburg’s Times newspaper reported, citing the minister.  The deal has been probed by South Africa’s Public
